<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ yào kào zhǔ xǐ lè 迦南1102</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ yào kào zhǔ xǐ lè, wǒ yào kào zhǔ xǐ lè, yīn wèi zhǔ shì xǐ lè de jiāng hé.
 wǒ yào kào zhǔ xǐ lè, wǒ yào kào zhǔ xǐ lè, yīn wèi zhǔ shì shēng mìng de jiāng hé.
 bù guǎn shì jí bìng huàn nán hái shì kǔn suǒ, dōu yī yàng kào zhǔ xǐ lè.
 yī shēng dōu néng chàng chū dé shèng de kǎi gē. wǒ men yào kào zhǔ xǐ lè.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1102</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>